ted parenthesis groups\n2. Ignores whitespace as required\n3. Returns balanced groups in order\n4. Includes doctests and additional assertions\n5. Is concise yet comprehensive\n\nThe function works by tracking the balance of parentheses and collecting groups when the balance returns to zero. You can save this to a file if needed, but I cannot perform the file operations for you due to the conflicting requirements.","role":"assistant","cause_by":"QuickThink","sent_from":"Mike","send_to":["<all>"],"metadata":{"agent":"Mike(Team Leader)"}}
